# 1 Minute | دقيقة واحدة

## Install & Run
- `cd one-minute`
- `npm install`
- `npm run dev` (Next.js dev server on http://localhost:3000)

## Editing Mock Data
- Update `src/app/api/posts/route.ts` to tweak categories, regions, or media.
- Keep `publishedAt` sorted newest-first and add new posts to the `RAW_POSTS` array.
- Use `lang: 'both'` for stories suitable for both languages.

## Connecting A Real Backend
1. Replace `/app/api/posts/route.ts` with fetches to your news API (REST/GraphQL).
2. Map backend payloads to the `Post` type; keep fields consistent with the UI.
3. Introduce ISR or streaming if the backend is slow; adjust `useInfinitePosts` to hit the new endpoint.
